1. *Najgore* je što ne znamo kuda dalje. (The worst thing is that we don't know what to do next.)

2. On je osećao da će mu *najgore* još tek da dođe. (He felt that the worst was yet to come.)

3. Što se tiče njegove situacije, *najgore* se već dogodilo. (As far as his situation was concerned, the worst had already happened.)

4. *Najgore* je što je izgubio svoje najbolje prijatelje. (The worst thing is that he lost his best friends.)

5. On je znao da će odluka koju će doneti imati *najgore* posledice. (He knew that the decision he was going to make would have the worst consequences.)